WEBVTT

00:02:28.738 --> 00:02:32.659
Their only job was
to break the plant apart

00:02:32.683 --> 00:02:34.083
and close it forever.

00:02:35.875 --> 00:02:37.855
I was met with a guy named Rich,

00:02:39.044 --> 00:02:40.221
the production manager.

00:02:41.256 --> 00:02:43.847
He offered to take me around,
show me around.

00:02:44.339 --> 00:02:45.506
He didn't say much,

00:02:45.530 --> 00:02:49.005
but around every corner,
he would point out some stories.

00:02:50.268 --> 00:02:52.347
Rich worked there for 20 years.

00:02:52.371 --> 00:02:54.585
His father made yogurt before him,

00:02:54.609 --> 00:02:57.264
and his grandfather
made cream cheese before that.

00:02:58.855 --> 00:03:02.808
You could tell that Rich felt guilty